Some cells i made for a prison break map

I know there are cells already but what sets these cells apart is the cool looking lasers

It's not well made but its decent you can make any changes possible

The lasers are guarded by invisable walls both ways so CTs nor Ts can mess around and plus lasers are 0 damage

I don't know, i couldn't think of a map so i made these heh :)

And if you use them i dont need credit but it would be nice =S Thanks
